{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Markdown is dying. And the people killing it... built Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c4f5acfdca8f5b55bc6007fb99e0ad95712e539df3225e61ca94838ea4710ce7",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Thariq works on Claude Code at Anthropic.",
      "checksum": "sha256:76731cbe3805934a80e88a0feeb4f8599f9aa0f16f70045ae522d37479f6f1a3",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Last week he dropped a thesis that broke the dev internet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8a4e9d47b5bec4c777c9363e51b80e773b23982a603ae5dc41aa2c8720b50301",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 18
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Seven hundred and fifty thousand views. Two point seven thousand likes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b1cb2cd2174e632e8f1b40d26b910787ed89b3fb6c284032780ad5087f80c0ed",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 29
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Three hundred forty reposts. And the replies are split.",
      "checksum": "sha256:57b1ba715e1aaaa50e26464d1443c63f4403d242d73d82f8e79d1ba8650924a9",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 40
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "But again and again, you see the same line.",
      "checksum": "sha256:257d8891e71c9af0fdbe16f3a5f0cb5442155c694f3f311a2010c43296b1d797",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 49
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Wait. You stopped too? He claims markdown is the wrong format for every spec, every plan, every P R writeup you hand to your agent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:70d8336b0a19aca076747f04734d28ebadf5b898fbb6fb4578af8c979394ebfa",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 8.962902494331066,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Almost all of it. Out. And he has the receipts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4a78fc090f8f7262bbf3af1836fac0a8c1c6f35467c73bc2880870b54d89a6f9",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 83
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "This is the unreasonable effectiveness of H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d60e3eedf156440ab3329ddf6b70bcaaa349be1d3ce0bf105a2ae1535572ef46",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 93
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "By the end of this video you will know exactly why your codebase is about to look very different.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1de7eb9ba96f9925c8f3a3edd96384f135bc0f46d2c4b1a34db9fb826088b501",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 5.851428571428571,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 103
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "And whether that is a good thing. Here is what H T M L can carry that markdown cannot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:699e4d36620aead41a1afce0c572887225fccfda50896c79459e244e3cea0d10",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 122
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "01. Information density. Markdown can carry headings.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c07b234683f29564391fb584805dcc5b8ea179cb0f7df33d2e6cc2b0a0ab0661",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 141
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Bold. A bullet list. A table if you squint at it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:62f23099424ff714a190b454423a5863c84a269586c0b53065faf28c953d8399",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 148
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "That is roughly it. H T M L can carry eight things in one file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1c66894b7cc43e92938f3961e226b7567a73ba5409940df96b13647d88254913",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 159
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Tables. C S S driven design. S V G illustrations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:71055541d1070a8e40e250dcd9c89320793ef536c8fe5d55eceabb4c65406edb",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 174
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Code snippets inside script tags. Live interactions wired with JavaScript and C S S.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bcb7c8d9429ffbd0336fd8eacf3b7ed6189be8b8cfe30ff22b0c10c31b46be04",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 184
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Workflows drawn with S V G and H T M L side by side.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c25e47663daf8e15ae5667427eb487c9a104924093f8e97172aeb02d2675b91",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 198
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Spatial data, anything you can place on a canvas with absolute positions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0cce07c6e165550fdf3ad7c6ac574c3034fb3bc6b6a9431c5b5add68ed8d24fe",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 212
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "And actual images, with image tags. Thariq's claim, and I think it holds \u2014 there is almost nothing Claude can read that you cannot represent in H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dc8cf686f28410909974d32691bb0ada9bdbe6995ff35b2a92efa0d1ab60bbc5",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 9.984580498866213,
      "word_count": 30,
      "words_offset": 224
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "So what does the model do when the format fails it?",
      "checksum": "sha256:a654b599e0b85ca7120e03fcdfca911168414ad0ae812510d7d6ece50da1af15",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 254
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "It improvises. ASCII diagrams. Or, his favorite, estimating colors with unicode characters.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fc79b1f9f41443d15323031d1c379a18f384fc25438c6dc42adeef04f058986f",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 5.851428571428571,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 265
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Boxes that pretend to be charts. Hashes that pretend to be color swatches.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dd388ef4df676b13aa31f035e78c6b43f5b1e28753d90874e0aaa5a086667e44",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 277
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "That is the cost of forcing a powerful agent through a format built for a 1990s readme.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e46538769e64616e05b94648a8e740c0957ce0530b78f5923d0e3c58ad0325a",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 290
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "When you give it H T M L, the agent stops faking the chart and just draws the chart.",
      "checksum": "sha256:04203f8acd63b7929d9652016a8271b518bd93c68212fadbbef0472d2c08c5d2",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 307
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "So compare. Same data, two formats. Markdown gives you this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:346b9b0962d81eec1c400ed9740a729be931b455266fb5fc83f9aa46ef42bbb0",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 326
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "A bar chart hand-drawn out of pipes and dashes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6034f4211625320dc4ae7039e901d5845e85b79d9d072ec73dc99c649db7e6be",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 336
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "From a distance it looks like a chart. Up close, the columns drift.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b1a89b34d85f39862615072cdf8f2fbd05ea855f9ab3065cae32c4cc869da76",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 345
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "The bars do not line up with the axis. And the second you paste it into a doc with a different font, every alignment breaks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b13207deef0aa12ac1109a7a369810ae57c873df72feea1ec6e4f96021552ce9",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 7.058866213151927,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 358
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "H T M L gives you this. Same five numbers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e969ff01d906c9792a1fb4a84520e4db01d6e15fb304df80eab9f6d64d592b63",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 383
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "A real S V G bar chart, rendered crisply, picking its own colors from a palette.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78a707c1a3a724dd3ee1628ff1487118122eb277b277d82b24abde8deaa35ff0",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 393
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Sitting inside a single dot h t m l file you can open in any browser.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e83cc3aead7f9af18bcf301930878f5a51cbbd4380983472260d117a75986571",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 409
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "That is why Thariq writes \u2014 H T M L documents are easier to read, easier to organize visually, easier to navigate with tabs and links and illustrations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2c7545523572f1bb1c0287572763e36afa6ce9dbf404c91471222b1423b98781",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 10.309659863945578,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 425
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "He says the chance someone actually reads your spec, your report, your P R writeup \u2014 that chance gets much, much higher when it is H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e6860d9e9123d05983b06ff7d1497734ab6bca8f62c84c00067303e76c8f357d",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 9.659501133786849,
      "word_count": 29,
      "words_offset": 453
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "A markdown file is a thing your colleague will skim.",
      "checksum": "sha256:63e00a44d52f13dca456716831b6dcfea69f001b27dc5fbf33f645347304003e",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 482
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "An H T M L file is a thing your colleague will open.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e1248567fa024c31862289e77fa748efb5ff6f46e3de305232e52d9eab32f0ed",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 492
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "That is the difference. And yes. There is a price.",
      "checksum": "sha256:885eaa7f571f6df03edb3708537e398d57b5b1b5eee9d4188d206ff4b7e24878",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 505
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "The honest one. H T M L can take two to four times longer to generate than markdown.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a055f57c65d584a2e76f1b9825e7e331734b77048f1e1dc419c1a53c908814f7",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 515
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Two to four x. That is real. But here is the piece that changes the math.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6bf8e6033fc658d047cbe147954d0ee643ca0d4d0ff59cb5a7366ea3c419dec8",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 533
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Opus 4.7 ships with a one million token context window.",
      "checksum": "sha256:072112f8a956dbdc251f2b4d5acdb02dc15276bf34eec52fdcec149ff9f86b5c",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 549
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "One million. Which means the extra tokens you spend rendering H T M L \u2014 they barely register against the budget you already have.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b7c82ddad87c4e81c917383d3180dd5ba829bde3c77ea707702deb313aedaf02",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 7.523265306122449,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 559
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "The cost is real. The cost is also absorbable.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5119689e91d826e9182cd2d638a71e1cc0c14bded22c5559454c0d3a2531ae9e",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 583
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "And in exchange you get a document your team will actually read.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a8df9dbe91e0fdc47f9c713d7d3b31e0700570f04494b440bcc700dae0a2d81",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 592
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Some of the replies under the post pushed back on this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:36d25afcb817932ecee0d1270a55869bd255c9e5261a101dcd01f45c1b52bdc2",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 604
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "They argued markdown's lower token spend is itself the value.",
      "checksum": "sha256:921299615e6404bab58798f6b6eeab0b051e3a63c672164529d4dda69b409800",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 615
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "The honest answer is \u2014 it depends what you are buying.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b3954e1fe557af831fe52824344495b0209f7ec5a34b561f7bbe00542df138d",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 625
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Here is the part that turns this from a thesis into a workflow.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eefad58e20dcf68a3141760900ebf8d3d805b657ce10bacce0e9d342380d0d3a",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 636
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Five places where switching to H T M L changes everything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:adbc7587416e9cf4b60094c2f94d3ada6bee8fbef5793cdd8a7797078dc9cd32",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 649
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "Use case one. Specs, planning, and exploration.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a9266c4adf011fefee5874975b5ebedc149196994d6074ba4fd39d1ee3f1843",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 660
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "You ask Claude Code to fan out six approaches to a problem in one H T M L file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1a6689f675b183e731096586a2626adf79b5fd2ac170cf5a4ea7cc45ad339a5d",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 667
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "Side by side. Each one labeled with the trade-off it is making.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7e7138db005da432f07a327b9c8570164b609af1388388fcf5e6cd847877e245",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 686
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "You pick. The pick becomes a plan with mockups and code snippets baked in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b92f090a5d6236f15c21b9ef9f5192177d6a439cb93111a887144fa6f19b24fd",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 698
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Use case two. Code review. The P R diff rendered with margin annotations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d1639f71e68bd34854cdcd19f72459132f4272af172b3119d21a3662fc83cb94",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 712
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "Severity colors. Jump links. Thariq attaches an H T M L code explainer to every P R he makes now \u2014 and he is on the team.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d168a74f308c776f4ac50fe13f468dca5baa71f09e7f28db121f233cc1c44a06",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 8.684263038548753,
      "word_count": 27,
      "words_offset": 725
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "He says it works better than the default GitHub diff view.",
      "checksum": "sha256:43dfdd63b64369b3a8bacfac50aed016751619a491c9fe0651275772701c79c0",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 752
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "Use case three. Design and prototypes. Claude Design is built on H T M L for a reason.",
      "checksum": "sha256:effccf7eb8ec8e2281cb8778d1e09388ef2ee6ea254ace1508e57a4134da952d",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 763
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "H T M L is incredibly expressive for design \u2014 even when your end surface is React, or Swift, or anything else.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5d800fa90f0f9708b61a3026d091a484fd6d7b992f783243ae85bc3aaf9dfc54",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 7.1053061224489795,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 781
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "Claude sketches in H T M L, then translates.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e02621379b4b3c943a52fa1569eb6baeec62d4c30987e0ff3d7e0e82440ead28",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 803
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "You can ship the prototype with sliders and knobs, tune the animation, then copy the parameters back into a prompt.",
      "checksum": "sha256:048594bf5fdcfb4218df4d6a14985552e4dc7c53375c0517871eea01617b1138",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 6.501587301587302,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 812
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "Use case four. Reports, research, and learning.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2cf3711f8a6aa7f196beef9d2fe66a13848ac9669a0704c689a608c88ce23312",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 832
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "You point Claude Code at your codebase, your git history, your Slack, the internet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:71c9ab25cfc65f458370900c2425797f2bb8406d4dffcc6c322b514721da56a8",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 839
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "You get back a single readable explainer page.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af767993a73799c142b90ea61bbd261336a715fc99b0dd6ca7c9a56edc010d0c",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 853
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "A diagram of the flow. Three or four key code snippets, annotated. A gotchas section at the bottom.",
      "checksum": "sha256:20a62a307553d3cd88f124d3edf466397357187d1b8340c9b77412499cd4bdc1",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 5.990748299319728,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 861
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "Use case five. Custom editing interfaces.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a4c2bee8a05d4191ec8c58be320c8f3a22ab4423e54614eb0ba029f678254423",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 879
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "This one is the sleeper. Sometimes typing in a text box cannot describe what you want.",
      "checksum": "sha256:677d23ebc743d3baf6dfc678c8cd6b06d46b0bdcdb0e702aa46c52800c96f322",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 885
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "So Claude Code builds you a throwaway editor.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9b07f13cd312647722f6d5baeaa8e0224c0ff655a081e8ae398aac4ecc3bbfcc",
      "wav": "chunk-64.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 901
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "text": "A single H T M L file purpose-built for your one piece of data.",
      "checksum": "sha256:89a3b5d03e540c448d37899eb6b0951a1e8035c930ff4491b8e60ae8b4f9e8cc",
      "wav": "chunk-65.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 909
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "text": "Drag thirty Linear tickets into now, next, later, cut.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c99e1e933d179f5dcebc313e7c90c57fba8f54c1cf5f27ab1aebd175decc7576",
      "wav": "chunk-66.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 923
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "text": "Edit a feature flag config with dependency warnings.",
      "checksum": "sha256:be2d386256cfa03cbf4966df736fa4329fd87d468fbd7ae27e131adea284dae8",
      "wav": "chunk-67.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 932
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "text": "Tune a system prompt with live re-render of three sample inputs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a6ec6a532b29b56a73963695f9b7f269959671428eb60a4ddbe7c40ff3ed08e",
      "wav": "chunk-68.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 940
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "text": "And every one of them ends with one button \u2014 copy it back out.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2b2da03173154873e4676edf4c13aec2d5afb80f809b066bfbcb86e68108f46d",
      "wav": "chunk-69.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 951
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "text": "As markdown. As a diff. As a prompt for the next session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d631516280e7256d32b9ad2b9f5f597c56bc983bd5573c693abfb5ce978fc0fc",
      "wav": "chunk-70.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 965
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "text": "So why Claude Code specifically? Why not Claude A I, or Claude Design?",
      "checksum": "sha256:f4776525ffe554d392778aa9a16b24b06b89893f532d47b1a62eb527bed9736d",
      "wav": "chunk-71.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 977
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "text": "Because of what Claude Code can ingest. Your filesystem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f6ff060bb7a594f1d4e1fd216dd75b567f0421c19a7bb2f600f00f4a8b45d6cf",
      "wav": "chunk-72.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 990
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "text": "Every dot h t m l file you have already generated, all visible at once.",
      "checksum": "sha256:33f8067d4fb1ceb25b3c99a167456f5aa33a2d4db25394b2599ddc0e7d27757a",
      "wav": "chunk-73.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 999
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "text": "Your M C P servers. Slack, Linear, anything you have connected.\n\nYour browser, when you have Claude in Chrome.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c309e74fa0d02741c069d51764041ec3cedade9772ccb049ec9eeb53e8a0cfc5",
      "wav": "chunk-74.wav",
      "duration": 6.733786848072563,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 1014
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "text": "Your git history. The why behind every line of code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e2d4cf9d415b26a97659d077ce3c33346b89989569210e874a19db3440cc427",
      "wav": "chunk-75.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1033
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "text": "That stack of context is what makes the H T M L output actually informed. The agent is not synthesizing in the dark \u2014 it is synthesizing from your real work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d4e396c8249f79fcc27124e698b9c4741dad86e3ba53b451fc774a3875c66575",
      "wav": "chunk-76.wav",
      "duration": 10.170340136054422,
      "word_count": 31,
      "words_offset": 1043
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "text": "Move the same prompt to a chat surface, and you lose half of it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:731135548d84fc7e228e4c6cff5fda6d08e2a38c6da5270767861873b10f9f2a",
      "wav": "chunk-77.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1074
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "text": "The artifact comes back generic. Pretty, maybe.",
      "checksum": "sha256:40ebd0ae620b1710ae090fc0ef51c7de2c0704dba13189a1796dcfd20f423b6e",
      "wav": "chunk-78.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1088
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "text": "But generic. This is the part that does not transfer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1cdf14a4305010e6d1607cd977ba833cf4a2b75c3da1fc9284b8325fb2bc3366",
      "wav": "chunk-79.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1095
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "text": "Claude Code's reach into your environment is the input that makes the output worth having.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7860bce94fc3b6f8d652527592acaf3f44970deac42f0468cba2795a717bb713",
      "wav": "chunk-80.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 1105
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "text": "Here is the part the article actually ends on.",
      "checksum": "sha256:238b96a15d8068fdd784bcc27a09d7aca34ddb7ae80537b6c78cbf71e9a0c013",
      "wav": "chunk-81.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1120
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "text": "Thariq says the real reason he switched is not density.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4af405b84ad37b41fe8e8c83bd3545bcd3bc71835153d305d76f9830ca8164c6",
      "wav": "chunk-82.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1129
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "text": "It is not sharing. It is not even the joy of making things.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8199e90c0d0b5485764a250953823b692fb8162fc558c65c5d4b4ec24244f9f1",
      "wav": "chunk-83.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1139
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "text": "It is that he stopped reading the markdown plans.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ca449d955e97632810d11f838f81adfab5aeee4b848cbe778fc3d0863b06693",
      "wav": "chunk-84.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1152
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "text": "He would offload work to Claude, get back a wall of text, and he just would not read it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:509b7f1a099158256b7bc12645f53985f6bb7d93e85b0385be7a962311f6ac1a",
      "wav": "chunk-85.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 1161
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "text": "Which meant he was leaving Claude to make every choice.",
      "checksum": "sha256:67263d799695b3c4c3d024577274d3e3e564e377b14fb40054e7f0c334713e6a",
      "wav": "chunk-86.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1180
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "text": "Which is a slow way to lose the plot. The H T M L versions \u2014 he reads them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ae38ae050556bc55bd8db1746e2e2ae0f4bc7123e628a21653476734be4aaf9e",
      "wav": "chunk-87.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 1190
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "text": "He clicks around. He suggests changes. He is back in the loop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:efd515b4b3105764367077fdffe104a1964644de8a9b150055ea96e126cd49da",
      "wav": "chunk-88.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 1209
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "text": "So I will let Thariq close it himself. I am happy to say I feel more in the loop than ever before when using H T M L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:10774bd02402a9f905316b3f842c0843f468e3a8d88c429c8d80e994dffbc97d",
      "wav": "chunk-89.wav",
      "duration": 7.1053061224489795,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 1221
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "text": "I hope you do too. The replies under the post are full of people saying the same thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dd501afda34d40f884bfc8735c8b2af5c3f2f100647454bb9d920bb13b9a3e60",
      "wav": "chunk-90.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1249
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "text": "I was already doing this, I just did not have the framing yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:876b681ad7af71a23d2070b97fd4753f6d34a716e9338207d40b5f511a547018",
      "wav": "chunk-91.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1267
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "text": "This finally explains why Claude keeps printing H T M L as artifacts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eeff9e2bad7e404cf4ec9ab95b3b7d9ef7a619a6c7615723d95e0d1b1f1fed95",
      "wav": "chunk-92.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1280
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "text": "I am moving my whole planning workflow today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:da1c52bbde0830ac2ed38cb6d33792e7e21fd81682966b57385324f67edc417c",
      "wav": "chunk-93.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1293
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "text": "You are going to see this format show up everywhere over the next few months.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8e8c70755c4cd39733cfe7e8036c1823eca17a19207792b669135c8d036a624c",
      "wav": "chunk-94.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 1301
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "text": "Specs. P R writeups. Status reports. Internal explainers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9bef28176d8685b22757922147b2ae58a8d432ef6688bdc57e9fab6f12165acc",
      "wav": "chunk-95.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1316
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "text": "Even editorial magazines \u2014 and judging by the replies, plenty of other places too.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b26214a8a9ed21d014635ba55fd1230217d5c7d7126dfd3009f1cd9ae8fb85ce",
      "wav": "chunk-96.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 1324
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "text": "Get ahead of it. Open one of the files in Thariq's gallery.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3dbe3fad3e1f7532ca76b1be5bd7c41421e4aa51ed4c88c3ab3b306b8fbac2e7",
      "wav": "chunk-97.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 1338
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "text": "Look at how it reads compared to the markdown you would normally get.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1b0a7d47c9ecb6701fc1c0fce09935885f08fee58841d409f1e02f89d9b9e494",
      "wav": "chunk-98.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1350
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "text": "And if you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous dot A I community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78a496825e21407cc57c48fc3f5123e9693a97210b1d579c87f18bf8eae48492",
      "wav": "chunk-99.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1363
    }
  ]
}